item.description: Former Congressional Candidate Mr. Bob Guida will be speaking and sharing a presentation for the group.  Former 1st Congressional District Mr. Rich Ashooh will be speaking and we are fortunate to have him agree to come and speak with us again.
item.why: Bob Guida is going to speak to our group upon his return from Bahrain. Rich Ashooh has agreed to speak with us as well. Bob Guida is a pilot and his schedule is always uncertain and we are hoping that he isn't called to fly during our meeting.
item.name: Bob Guida and Rich Ashooh to speak at Regular 912 Meeting
